channel.title: Fluex - Wings to Fly REMAKE CHALLENGE
channel.description:
I am making. This will consist of crating a remake of a song I slightly adore. This song is called Wings to Fly by Fluex, and the link for listening to the song is https://m.soundcloud.com/thisisfrequency/fluex-wings-to-fly
There are no requirements for this, and you can choose how much of the song you want done. Because it might take a while, I’ll be judging by early March.
